                    <div class="steps-heading">
                        <h2>Steps to adopt a child</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="steps-para">
                        <p>Are you thinking of adopting a child in India? There are a few steps to follow through but worry not; the adoption process is straightforward and not as complicated as you may think.</p>
                        <p>Adopting a child can be an enormously enriching experience and Adpot-a-Need invites families from all ethnic groups and backgrounds.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="main-steps">
                        
                        <div class="dropdown-container">
                            <div class="dropdown-header" onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">
                                <h3>Step 1: Enquiry</h3>
                                <span class="dropdown-icon">+</span>
                                <!-- <a href="" class="step-info"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></a> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="dropdown-content">
                                <p>Contact us to discuss your interest in adoption. We will provide you with information about the adoption process and answer any questions you may have.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>


                        <div class="dropdown-container">
                            <div class="dropdown-header" onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">
                                <h3>Step 2: Application</h3>
                                <span class="dropdown-icon">+</span>
                                <!-- <a href="" class="step-info"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></a> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="dropdown-content">
                                <p>Complete an adoption application form and provide us with the necessary documentation, including identification, proof of income, and references.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="dropdown-container">
                            <div class="dropdown-header" onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">
                                <h3>Step 3: Home Study</h3>
                                <span class="dropdown-icon">+</span>
                                <!-- <a href="" class="step-info"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></a> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="dropdown-content">
                                <p>A social worker will visit your home to assess your suitability as an adoptive parent. This includes interviews, background checks, and a review of your living situation.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="dropdown-container">
                            <div class="dropdown-header" onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">
                                <h3>Step 4: Child Matching</h3>
                                <span class="dropdown-icon">+</span>
                                <!-- <a href="" class="step-info"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></a> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="dropdown-content">
                                <p>Once your home study is approved, we will work to match you with a child who meets your preferences and needs.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="dropdown-container">
                            <div class="dropdown-header" onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">
                                <h3>Step 5: Placement</h3>
                                <span class="dropdown-icon">+</span>
                                <!-- <a href="" class="step-info"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></a> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="dropdown-content">
                                <p>Once a match is made, you will be given the opportunity to meet the child and spend time together before the placement is finalized.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="dropdown-container">
                            <div class="dropdown-header" onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">
                                <h3>Step 6: Finalization</h3>
                                <span class="dropdown-icon">+</span>
                                <!-- <a href="" class="step-info"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></a> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="dropdown-content">
                                <p>After a period of supervision, the adoption will be finalized in court, and you will become the legal parent of the child.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>  
                        
                        <div class="dropdown-container">
                            <div class="dropdown-header" onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">
                                <h3>Step 7: Post-Adoption Support</h3>
                                <span class="dropdown-icon">+</span>
                                <!-- <a href="" class="step-info"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></a> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="dropdown-content">
                                <p>We provide ongoing support to adoptive families, including counseling, support groups, and resources to help you navigate the challenges of adoption.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="dropdown-container">
                            <div class="dropdown-header" onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">
                                <h3>Step 8: Celebration</h3>
                                <span class="dropdown-icon">+</span>
                                <!-- <a href="" class="step-info"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></a> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="dropdown-content">
                                <p>Celebrate the joy of adoption with your new family member and create lasting memories together.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="dropdown-container">
                            <div class="dropdown-header" onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">
                                <h3>Step 9: Stay Connected</h3>
                                <span class="dropdown-icon">+</span>
                                <!-- <a href="" class="step-info"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></a> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="dropdown-content">
                                <p>Stay connected with us and other adoptive families through our community events and activities.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div> 
                    </div>
